  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>The luxurious Hotel Berghof is one of <a data-udi="umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0c1aff3b3b645fbaf04f9ae393281d6}" title="Lech">Lech’s</a> leading hotels and is full of Austrian charm thanks to the hospitable Burger family.</span></p>
<h2><span>Private lift</span></h2>
<p><span>Located right above the centre of Lech, you have your own private lift that takes you </span><span>from the hotel</span><span> into the resort centre and the main ski lifts.</span></p>
<p>The hotel is comfortably and stylishly decorated and enjoys superb views from its enviable position above the village centre.</p>
<h2><span>It's in the details</span></h2>
<p><span>This charming hotel offers the top level of service you would expect, with an immensely personal touch. The staff are dedicated to the details and could not be more helpful and warm throughout your stay.</span></p>
<h2><span>Fine dining</span></h2>
<p>Hotel Berghof prides itself on providing exquisite food. A five course nouvelle cuisine style meal awaits you in the evening and once a week you can enjoy a speciality buffet and candlelit gala dinner with piano music. If you fancy something different you can even enjoy a fondue evening on request.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Berghof making us the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
