  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Arlberg </strong>Austrian twin rooms are around <span>25m² and individually styled. These rooms have a bath and sleep up to two adults.</span></p>
<p><strong>Hasenfluh</strong> Austrian twins rooms are also around 25m<span>². These rooms have a shower, lounge area and south facing balcony. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</span></p>
<p><strong>Omeshorn </strong>Austrian twin rooms are around <span>36m². Also with a lounge area and south facing balcony. These rooms sleep up to four, using the additional double sofa bed.</span></p>
<p><strong>Schafberg</strong> Austrian twin rooms are around 42m<span>² and also sleep up top four. The rooms benefit from additional amenities including tea and coffee making facilities but are on request, please call to book.</span></p>
<p><strong>Single rooms </strong>are located in an annex connected to the main hotel by corridor. They are around 20-25m<span>² with shower.</span></p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
